{"books":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":[""],"article":{"title":"鸣放诗——给一年级的某几个团支委","authors":["中央民族学院","王成良"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":3}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"text":"鸣放诗——给一年级的某几个团支委","type":"title"},{"text":"中央民族学院王成良","type":"authors"},{"text":"（王成良：中央民族学院语文系一年级藏语班学生）","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"给一年级的某几个团支委    汪洋(王成良)","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"团的三大白白隆重的：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"以共青团员的桂冠为你们加冕","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"而在冲洗“祖国灵魂”的风雨中","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你们却像企鹅一样躲在岩石底下","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"却像潜水鸟一样藏的海底深渊。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"大字报的海涛中","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"也有你们的两张","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但却是哭诉自己的清白。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"小字报的雪片中","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"也有你们的一份","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但是却成惶成恐的向上司表白忠孝心肝。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"背后，你们也嘁嘁喳喳开过会，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但却是审判那些","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——勇敢的飞掠着、高唱着、呼唤风雨的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——擦伤了你们皮毛的海燕。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们语文系的梁柱，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"可以任其虫蛙和腐毁；","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们语文系的“阶级头×”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"可以任其生赘和毒瘤癌，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但你们的名誉地位、晋升前途","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"必须要保全","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"所以你们跌跤在几个支委的周围","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"阿谀谗佞，明哲保身、缄然不言，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"好吧，明天","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"前世界残存的魑魅，魍魉","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"将以八抬大轿","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"把你们抬向黄龙白虎的衙殿","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但千万不要带头","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"纯洁荣耀的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“共产主义战士”的桂冠。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":" (录自“野草”第3期)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"王士镇的发言    汪洋(王成良)","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"会场","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你愤怒的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"海面","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"激忿的浪花","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不断涌现","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"是谁?一跃","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"站在了","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"冲天大浪的尖端","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"紧撕着","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"施飞乌云的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"边沿","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"喷吐着","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"心血和热泪","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"向苍天呼唤","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“天！","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"天啊！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我的天！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"请把你","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"日益窥视大地的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"双眼","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"瞪向这","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"频临枯荒的土山","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"让闪电","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"击倒那","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一手遮天的腹内空虚的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"古木吧！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"让暴雨","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"冲醒那","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不学无术揠苗助长的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"伪农吧！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们要园丁","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"阳光","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"雨露","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"春天！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"雷霆呵","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"替我们全宇宙","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"呼喊","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"救救孩子吧","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"救","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"救","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"孩子！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们这些枯瘦干瘪的孤儿","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"要成长","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"生存发展！！”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"骤然","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"象把乌云撕破","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"掌声象","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"暴雨突降一般","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"掌声!","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"掌声!","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"掌声!","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"响彻了","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这群孤儿的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"心田。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":" (录自“野草”第3期)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":" 来源：《关于“野草”、“蜜蜂”社反动小集团的材料》，中共中央民族学院整风办公室编，1957年12月。","type":"paragraph"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":0,"page_end":0,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}